            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指回升171點報27094點 攜程低開0.65%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段回升，再度升越兩萬七關口。恒生指數開市報27094點，升171點或0.64%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5883點，升55點或0.94%；國企指數以9330點開市，升63點或0.68%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天急挫的攜程(09961)今早略為低開，以457元開市，微跌0.65%。其他重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報167.9元，升2.01%；騰訊(00700)開報627元，升0.8%；滙控(00005)開報129元，也升0.62%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_攜程集團09961-4-官網影片截圖.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_攜程集團09961-4-官網影片截圖.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多家公司本身或股東配股，相關股份今早普遍偏軟。其中藥明生物(02269)股東配股套現，該股今早開報38.66元，跌3.4%；優然牧業(09858)向大股東及投資者配股，該股今早開報4.08元，亦跌5.12%；半新股雲知聲(09678)配股籌逾1.9億元，該股今早以300元開市，暫時無升跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">快手(01024)落實發行優先票據規模，該股今早開報80.85元，升1.64%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">洛陽鉬業(03993)發盈喜，該股今早開報22.62元，升0.98%；六福集團(00590)公布上季銷售成績，該股今早開報27.4元，升0.37%；李寧(02331)上季零售流水按年錄低單位數跌幅，該股今早開市仍升1.74%，報19.89元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15586614-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87171%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b127094%e9%bb%9e-%e6%94%9c%e7%a8%8b%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b0-65",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 09:30:26",
