            "title": "即月期指大幅高開重越兩萬七 報27141點 高水217點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期指跟隨外圍大幅高開，重越兩萬七關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報27141點，升208點，較上日現貨收市價26923點高水217點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5890點，升56點，高水62點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9339點，升68點，高水72點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15586592-%e5%8d%b3%e6%9c%88%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%87%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83-%e5%a0%b127141%e9%bb%9e-%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4217%e9%bb%9e",
